| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3246 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a6cc7d3b-7266-52bc-94e6-6ad0cdd5cb75"
